These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, house, blues, salsa
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | blues | house | jazz | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, lizard, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | goldfish | lizard | ferret | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, singing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | singing | chess | drawing | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, subway, helicopter, ship
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
